---
import { IoPricetag } from "react-icons/io5"
import { TbLabelImportantFilled } from "react-icons/tb"
---
<div class="flex flex-col gap-y-3.5 items-center justify-center px-4 md:px-10 my-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-start md:text-center gap-y-2 px-4 md:my-8">
    <h3 class="text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl 2xl:text-5xl font-bold font-poppins">SMS verification that <span class="font-black">JUST</span> works.</h3>
    <p class="text-zinc-100 text-sm xl:text-base 2xl:text-lg max-w-xl 2xl:max-w-2xl">
        From signup to verification code, AlteraSMS makes the process of verifying your accounts simple and efficient. Explore our key features designed to streamline your experience.
    </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 grid-rows-2 md:grid-cols-2 md:grid-rows-1 gap-4">
    <img src="/numbers.png" alt="Picture of numbers listed on our dashboard" class="select-none" />
    <div class="flex flex-col md:justify-evenly gap-y-8 md:gap-y-4 md:-mt-3">
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-x-2.5">
        <TbLabelImportantFilled className="shrink-0 mt-2 size-7 xl:size-9 text-cyan-400" />
        <div>
            <h4 class="text-zinc-100 text-lg xl:text-xl font-semibold">High Quality Numbers</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-200 text-sm xl:text-base">
            We provide high-quality non-VoiP numbers <strong>guaranteed to satisfy your verification needs</strong>. If your number doesn't meet security requirements, don't worry, we <strong>only charge when your number receives a message</strong> from your requested service.
            </p>
        </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-x-2.5">
        <IoPricetag className="shrink-0 mt-2 size-7 xl:size-9 text-cyan-400" />
        <div>
            <h4 class="text-zinc-100 text-lg xl:text-xl font-semibold">Fixed Pricing</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-200 text-sm xl:text-base">
            Our numbers stay at their prices even when they are in high demand. AlteraSMS prides itself on always offering you with great deals that never change!
            </p>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</div>